33
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:14,640
Bukan dia yang kumaksud, tapi aku.

34
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:17,560
Kau kenapa?

35
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:24,160
Xue Muyun, dia...

36
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:27,720
- Xue Muyun?
- Dia...

37
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,600
Tatapan matanya kepadaku

38
